          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Charitable Giving Tax Deduction Act </b></p> <p>This bill modifies the requirements for calculating taxable income to allow a deduction from gross income (above-the-line deduction) for charitable contributions that are allowed as an itemized deduction under current law. </p>]]>
        </text>
